#Install

  KXL library 1.0.0 or more Vers are required.
  Please install beforehand.
  (http://www2.mwnet.or.jp/~fc3srx7)

  tar xzvf geki2-KXL-xxxx.tar.gz(xxxx is version)
  cd geki2-KXL-xxxx
  ./configure
  make
  make install
  geki2 & return It starts. 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
#key operation

  cursor up    - It moves upward.
  cursor down  - It moves downward.
  cursor left  - It moves to the left.
  cursor right - It moves to the right.
  'z'          - discharges arms.
  's'          - pause.
                 'z' - return.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
#Power up items.

[S] ball  - shot power up.
[L] ball  - laser power up.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
